item.title: 6 Alarming Symptoms Of Tonsilloliths That Should Never Be Ignored
item.description: Ever experience a sore throat but think there could be more to it than having strep throat or tonsillitis? Maybe you’ve noticed your tonsils are swollen or you see something strange at the back of your throat.
